name: AAA Logo
description: AAA Logo is a logo designer with more than 2,000 logo subjects and cliparts. It takes a simple yet powerful way to design professional logos. All bulit-in logo subjects are vector-based and can be easily resized and rotated, and can apply different styles on any single subject.

zh_CN.description: AAA Logo是一款Logo设计软件，通过简单而强大的方式设计专业的Logo，其中自带2000多个Logo对象和剪贴画的图库。所有内置Logo对象都是基于矢量的，可以轻易的缩放和旋转，也可以对任意单独对象应用不同的样式。
zh_CN.name: AAA Logo
